Ji Yunlei deixou o Starlight Group
e fundou a Dafu Jewelry.

00:16:20.620 --> 00:16:22.860
Mais tarde, quando os planos de Ye Taiting
vieram a público,

00:16:23.260 --> 00:16:24.820
Ye Xiaoting descobriu.

00:16:25.820 --> 00:16:27.620
